t nhau. Liệu cuộc chiến 30 năm của họ còn kéo dài bao lâu? Họ có vì con cái mà giải hòa hay con cái của họ phải hy sinh tình cảm vì đấng sinh thành?</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"109705","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2025-01-02T11:19:44.000Z","cast":["Liza Wong Ming-Chuen","Gigi Wong","Tiền Gia Lạc","La Trọng Khiêm","Mandy Wong","Eliza Sam","Lý Thành Xương","Mimi Chu Mai-Mai","Chung King-Fai","Jerry Koo Ming-Wah","Janice Shum","Cecilia So Yan-Chee","Ngai Wai-Man","Zhang Huiwen","Eddy Law Tin-Chi"],"director":["Phan Gia Đức"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Liza Wong Ming-Chuen","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Liza Wong Ming-Chuen","tmdb_id":240159,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oElwuzlAtF5VobV0ElRt0ZvW5gN.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/240159"},{"name":"Gigi Wong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Gigi Wong","tmdb_id":1140989,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kdq98Xdx8yfUuhPZIHbRHrqnk3n.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1140989"},{"name":"Tiền Gia Lạc","name_vi":"Tiền Gia Lạc","name_original":"Chin Ka-Lok","tmdb_id":148884,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1C8uMztrOOBYlhOj2VKHsfDzQv9.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/148884"},{"name":"La Trọng Khiêm","name_vi":"La Trọng Khiêm","name_original":"Lo Chung-Him","tmdb_id":237032,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dAc0eHm0CWBBu7L8KD84RrHAZyo.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/237032"},{"name":"Mandy Wong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Mandy Wong","tmdb_id":1255464,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hK69LsDU6G1EHtiwPEpf7BYV0e.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1255464"},{"name":"Eliza Sam","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Eliza Sam","tmdb_id":1688880,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cBjklXUuITK69b75HaEVltOdwnC.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1688880"},{"name":"Lý Thành Xương","name_vi":"Lý Thành Xương","name_original":"Lee Shing-Cheong","tmdb_id":14